quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,122,"Imirwi ibiri yo muri mwebwe mugihe yitegurira kugira ubwoba n’Imana ica iba umuhagarikizi wiyo mirwi yose uko ari ibiri, naba Isilamu aho bari nibizere Imana yabo gusa"
  3,123,"N’Imana niyo yabarokoye mungwano ya Badru, mugihe ata bushobozi mwari mufise, rero nimutinye Imana yanyu kugira ngo mushobore kuyikengurukira"
  3,124,"Mugihe yabwira aba Isilamu ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimuhagijwe n’Imana yanyu, mugihe yobafashisha Abamarayika ibihumbi bitatu bazoba bamanuwe nayo"
  3,125,"Egome, nimwigumya n’ukwirinda n’ivyabujijwe nayo n’ukubashikira n’ingoga na n’ingoga, aho niho Imana yanyu izo bafasha kubamarayika ibihumbi bitanu basatira n’inguvu nyinshi cane"
  3,126,"N’Imana ntiyagize ibi vyose atari uko ari ibimenyetso kuri mwebwe kugira ngo imitima yanyu ishobore guhumura kuriyo, n’imfashanyo ntisohoka atari kububasha bw’Imana kuko niyo ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  3,127,"Kugira ngo ice kimwe mu bihimba vyo muri bamwe bahemukiye Imana yabo y’ukuri, canke ibatetereze kugira ngo bashobore kugaruka bamaze gutsindwa"
  3,128,"Wewe\tntanakimwe\tufise\tmuri\tizi\tmpanuro,\tcanke\tngo\tubagirire ikigongwe canke ngo ubahane, kuko n’abantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  3,129,"Vyose\tnivy’Imana\tgusa\tibiri\tmu\tMajuru\tn’ibiri\tkw’Isi,\trero\tigirira ikigongwe kuwo yishakiye n’uguhana uwo yishakiye, n’Imana\tniyo nyene imbabazi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  3,130,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimurye amatungo y’umurengero, mukaguma mwongereza ayo matungo kuyandi, kandi mutinye Imana yanyu kugira ngo mushobore gutunganirwa"
  3,131,Kandi mutinye umucanwa wabikiwe abahakanyi bahakanye amategeko y’Imana
  3,132,Kandi mutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo kugira ngo muronke impuhwe zayo